&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://developers.google.com/protocol-buffers/docs/proto3#scalar&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;string&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br/&gt; Optional error message that contains more details about the error that occurred.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
&lt;p&gt;–&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
